    {
      "id": "2022-r1-phys-1",
      "number": "I-A 问1",
      "topic": "两根绳的静力平衡",
      "topicTag": "力学·静力平衡",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "如图，用两根轻绳 A、B 从天花板悬挂小物体。绳 A 与水平方向成 $60°$，绳 B 与水平方向成 $45°$。设绳 A、B 的张力分别为 $T_A$、$T_B$，求 $T_A/T_B$。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{\\sqrt2}{2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\sqrt2$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$1$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{\\sqrt6}{3}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{\\sqrt6}{2}$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2022_R1_physics/q01.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "小物体静止，水平方向合力为 0。比较两根绳张力的水平分量即可求出比值。",
        "analysis": "水平方向上，绳 A 的水平分量大小为 $T_A\\cos60°$，绳 B 的水平分量大小为 $T_B\\cos45°$。二者相等。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 写出水平方向平衡",
            "content": "$$T_A\\cos60°=T_B\\cos45°$$\n\n代入\n\n$$\\cos60°=\\frac12,\\quad \\cos45°=\\frac{\\sqrt2}{2}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 求张力比",
            "content": "$$T_A\\cdot\\frac12=T_B\\cdot\\frac{\\sqrt2}{2}$$\n\n所以\n\n$$\\frac{T_A}{T_B}=\\sqrt2$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "② $\\dfrac{T_A}{T_B}=\\sqrt2$",
        "correctOption": "②"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2022-r1-phys-2",
      "number": "I-B 问2",
      "topic": "斜面连接体的加速度",
      "topicTag": "力学·牛顿运动定律",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "如图，直角三角形台的三边长为 $3L,4L,5L$，质量均为 $m$ 的小物体 A、B 分别放在两侧光滑斜面上，并用跨过轻滑轮的轻绳连接。释放后 A、B 做等加速度运动，求加速度大小 $a$。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{3}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{4}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{5}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{6}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{8}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑦",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{10}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑧",
          "content": "$\\dfrac{g}{12}$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2022_R1_physics/q02.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "两侧斜面的倾角由 $3:4:5$ 三角形决定。沿斜面的重力分量不同，其差提供两个物体整体的加速度。",
        "analysis": "左侧 $4L$ 斜面的竖直升高为 $3L$，所以 $\\sin\\alpha=3/5$；右侧 $3L$ 斜面的竖直升高为 $4L$，所以 $\\sin\\beta=4/5$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 求两侧重力沿斜面分量",
            "content": "A 所在斜面：\n\n$$mg\\sin\\alpha=mg\\cdot\\frac35$$\n\nB 所在斜面：\n\n$$mg\\sin\\beta=mg\\cdot\\frac45$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 对整体列运动方程",
            "content": "B 一侧的分力较大，因此 B 下滑、A 上滑。对 A、B 整体：\n\n$$mg\\frac45-mg\\frac35=2ma$$\n\n$$\\frac15mg=2ma$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 求加速度",
            "content": "$$a=\\frac{g}{10}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "⑦ $a=\\dfrac{g}{10}$",
        "correctOption": "⑦"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2022-r1-phys-3",
      "number": "I-C 问3",
      "topic": "粗糙斜面上的动摩擦力",
      "topicTag": "力学·摩擦·运动图像",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "质量 $2.0\\,\\mathrm{kg}$ 的小物体沿与水平面成 $30°$ 的粗糙斜面下滑。图像给出了沿斜面向下为正的速度 $v$ 与时间 $t$ 的关系。取 $g=9.8\\,\\mathrm{m/s^2}$，求动摩擦力大小。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$1.9\\,\\mathrm{N}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$3.8\\,\\mathrm{N}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$5.5\\,\\mathrm{N}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$7.0\\,\\mathrm{N}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$11\\,\\mathrm{N}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$14\\,\\mathrm{N}$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2022_R1_physics/q03.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "速度-时间图像的斜率就是加速度。沿斜面方向，重力分力向下，动摩擦力向上。",
        "analysis": "图像斜率约为 $3.0\\,\\mathrm{m/s^2}$。沿斜面方向列式 $mg\\sin30°-f=ma$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 由图像求加速度",
            "content": "$$a=\\frac{\\Delta v}{\\Delta t}=\\frac{9.0}{3.0}=3.0\\,\\mathrm{m/s^2}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 沿斜面列方程",
            "content": "$$mg\\sin30°-f=ma$$\n\n$$2.0\\times9.8\\times\\frac12-f=2.0\\times3.0$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 求摩擦力",
            "content": "$$9.8-f=6.0$$\n\n$$f=3.8\\,\\mathrm{N}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "② $3.8\\,\\mathrm{N}$",
        "correctOption": "②"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2022-r1-phys-4",
      "number": "I-D 问4",
      "topic": "一维碰撞的反发系数",
      "topicTag": "力学·动量·碰撞",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "质量 $m$ 的小物体 A 以速度 $v$ 向右运动，质量 $\\dfrac{3m}{2}$ 的小物体 B 以速度 $\\dfrac{v}{3}$ 向左运动。碰撞后 A 静止。求碰撞的反发系数 $e$。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$0$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\dfrac16$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\dfrac15$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\dfrac14$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\dfrac13$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$\\dfrac25$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑦",
          "content": "$\\dfrac12$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑧",
          "content": "$1$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2022_R1_physics/q04.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "先用动量守恒求碰撞后 B 的速度，再用分离速度与接近速度之比求反发系数。",
        "analysis": "取向右为正。碰撞前总动量为 $mv-\\frac{3m}{2}\\cdot\\frac{v}{3}=\\frac12mv$。碰撞后 A 静止，所以 B 向右速度为 $v/3$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 用动量守恒求 B 的末速度",
            "content": "设碰撞后 B 的速度为 $u$：\n\n$$mv-\\frac{3m}{2}\\cdot\\frac{v}{3}=\\frac{3m}{2}u$$\n\n$$\\frac12mv=\\frac{3m}{2}u$$\n\n$$u=\\frac{v}{3}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 求反发系数",
            "content": "碰撞前接近速度为\n\n$$v-\\left(-\\frac{v}{3}\\right)=\\frac{4v}{3}$$\n\n碰撞后分离速度为\n\n$$\\frac{v}{3}-0=\\frac{v}{3}$$\n\n所以\n\n$$e=\\frac{v/3}{4v/3}=\\frac14$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "④ $e=\\dfrac14$",
        "correctOption": "④"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2022-r1-phys-5",
      "number": "I-E 问5",
      "topic": "圆锥面内的等速圆周运动",
      "topicTag": "力学·圆周运动",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "小物体在固定的光滑圆锥面内侧做水平面内半径为 $r$、速率为 $v$ 的等速圆周运动。小物体与顶点连线和中心轴的夹角为 $\\theta$。求 $r,v,\\theta$ 的关系。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$\\sin\\theta=\\dfrac{gr}{v^2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{gr}{v^2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\tan\\theta=\\dfrac{gr}{v^2}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\sin\\theta=\\dfrac{v^2}{gr}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{v^2}{gr}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$\\tan\\theta=\\dfrac{v^2}{gr}$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2022_R1_physics/q05.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "圆锥面对物体的支持力可以分解为竖直分量和水平分量。竖直分量平衡重力，水平分量提供向心力。",
        "analysis": "支持力 $N$ 的竖直分量为 $N\\sin\\theta$，水平分量为 $N\\cos\\theta$，于是 $N\\sin\\theta=mg$，$N\\cos\\theta=mv^2/r$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 竖直方向平衡",
            "content": "$$N\\sin\\theta=mg$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 水平方向提供向心力",
            "content": "$$N\\cos\\theta=\\frac{mv^2}{r}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 两式相除",
            "content": "$$\\frac{N\\sin\\theta}{N\\cos\\theta}=\\frac{mg}{mv^2/r}$$\n\n$$\\tan\\theta=\\frac{gr}{v^2}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "③ $\\tan\\theta=\\dfrac{gr}{v^2}$",
        "correctOption": "③"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2022-r1-phys-6",
      "number": "I-F 问6",
      "topic": "人造卫星的圆周运动",
      "topicTag": "力学·万有引力",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "把地球看成半径为 $R$ 的球，地表重力加速度为 $g$。人造卫星绕地球中心做半径 $3R$、速率 $v$ 的等速圆周运动。求 $v$。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$\\sqrt{\\dfrac{gR}{2}}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$\\sqrt{\\dfrac{gR}{3}}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\sqrt{\\dfrac{gR}{4}}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$\\sqrt{gR}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\sqrt{2gR}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$\\sqrt{3gR}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑦",
          "content": "$\\sqrt{4gR}$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2022_R1_physics/q06.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "距地心 $3R$ 处的重力加速度是地表的 $1/9$。该引力加速度提供向心加速度。",
        "analysis": "在轨道半径 $3R$ 处，$g'=g/9$。圆周运动满足 $v^2/(3R)=g/9$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 求轨道处引力加速度",
            "content": "$$g'=g\\left(\\frac{R}{3R}\\right)^2=\\frac{g}{9}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 列向心加速度关系",
            "content": "$$\\frac{v^2}{3R}=\\frac{g}{9}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 求速率",
            "content": "$$v^2=\\frac{gR}{3}$$\n\n$$v=\\sqrt{\\frac{gR}{3}}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "② $v=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{gR}{3}}$",
        "correctOption": "②"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2022-r1-phys-7",
      "number": "II-A 问1",
      "topic": "冰、水、水蒸气的热量计算",
      "topicTag": "热学·热量与状态变化",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "$0°C$ 的冰 $10\\,\\mathrm{g}$ 每秒吸收 $300\\,\\mathrm{J}$ 的热量，先全部变成 $0°C$ 的水，再继续吸热全部变成 $100°C$ 的水蒸气。冰的熔解热为 $3.4\\times10^2\\,\\mathrm{J/g}$，水的比热为 $4.2\\,\\mathrm{J/(g\\cdot K)}$，水的蒸发热为 $2.3\\times10^3\\,\\mathrm{J/g}$。求总时间。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$2.0\\times10^1\\,\\mathrm{s}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$4.0\\times10^1\\,\\mathrm{s}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$6.0\\times10^1\\,\\mathrm{s}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$8.0\\times10^1\\,\\mathrm{s}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$1.0\\times10^2\\,\\mathrm{s}$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑥",
          "content": "$1.2\\times10^2\\,\\mathrm{s}$"
        }
      ],
      "solution": {
        "translation": "总热量包含熔化、从 $0°C$ 加热到 $100°C$、汽化三部分。再除以每秒供热量。",
        "analysis": "熔化需 $3400\\,\\mathrm{J}$，升温需 $4200\\,\\mathrm{J}$，汽化需 $23000\\,\\mathrm{J}$，合计 $30600\\,\\mathrm{J}$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 熔化所需热量",
            "content": "$$Q_1=10\\times3.4\\times10^2=3.4\\times10^3\\,\\mathrm{J}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 水升温所需热量",
            "content": "$$Q_2=10\\times4.2\\times100=4.2\\times10^3\\,\\mathrm{J}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 汽化所需热量",
            "content": "$$Q_3=10\\times2.3\\times10^3=2.3\\times10^4\\,\\mathrm{J}$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(4) 求时间",
            "content": "$$Q=3.4\\times10^3+4.2\\times10^3+2.3\\times10^4=3.06\\times10^4\\,\\mathrm{J}$$\n\n$$t=\\frac{3.06\\times10^4}{300}=102\\,\\mathrm{s}\\approx1.0\\times10^2\\,\\mathrm{s}$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "⑤ $1.0\\times10^2\\,\\mathrm{s}$",
        "correctOption": "⑤"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2022-r1-phys-8",
      "number": "II-B 问2",
      "topic": "定压加热与定容加热",
      "topicTag": "热学·理想气体",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "绝热气缸中封入单原子分子理想气体，用气缸内加热器从 $t=0$ 开始以恒定功率加热。气体缓慢膨胀，活塞在 $t=t_A$ 到达挡块 A，之后活塞静止。问气体温度 $T$ 与时间 $t$ 的图像。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$t_A$ 前温度一定，$t_A$ 后线性上升"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$t_A$ 前线性上升，$t_A$ 后温度一定"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$t_A$ 前线性上升，$t_A$ 后斜率变大"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$t_A$ 前线性上升，$t_A$ 后斜率变小"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2022_R1_physics/q08.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "活塞碰到挡块前，气体近似定压膨胀；碰到挡块后体积固定，变成定容加热。",
        "analysis": "恒定功率下，$\\Delta T=Q/(nC)$。定压时使用 $C_p$，定容时使用 $C_v$。单原子理想气体 $C_p>C_v$，所以定容阶段温度上升更快。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) $t_A$ 前是定压过程",
            "content": "活塞缓慢移动，外界大气压一定，所以气体定压膨胀。恒定功率加热时\n\n$$Q=nC_p\\Delta T$$\n\n因此 $T$ 随 $t$ 线性增加。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) $t_A$ 后是定容过程",
            "content": "活塞被挡块固定，体积不再变化：\n\n$$Q=nC_v\\Delta T$$\n\n因为 $C_v<C_p$，同样热量造成的温度升高更大。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 判断图像",
            "content": "所以 $t_A$ 前后都是直线，但 $t_A$ 后斜率变大。对应选项 ③。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "③ $t_A$ 后斜率变大",
        "correctOption": "③"
      }
    },
